name: AFR Cover: 18 Jan 2022
description:
Own one of ten digital copies of the front cover to the Australian Financial Review
published on the 18th January 2022. Featured articles include the cancellation of Novak
Djokovic’s Australian visa on the grounds of public interest. This follows a string of
negotiations between Novak and the Australian government, prompted by the tennis
star’s vaccination status amidst the COVID-19 pandemic.
